WorldCom Project:

In order to execute all these little programs you will need next libraries:
(needed in your environment using Anaconda or using PIP in your system)
-	random
-	numpy
-	datetime
-	math
-	pandas
-	matplotlib
-	csv
-	requests
-	lxml (To macOS you will need to install it)
-	beautifulsoup4 o bs4.
-	nltk (Once you installed the library, install package ‘stop_words’ de “spanish” or "english" depends on the language you are working on to save the unrelevant words).
-	stop-words  (bs4 package to generate the unuseful words).
-	mrjob

Installation:
Outside Python from cmd or Command line Terminal (Linux/Mac users): 

>> Pip3 install “library”

Programs:
Inside any function or .py file there is a chunk which imports the libraries needed.
-	Next file doesn't bring any result when are running from console or Terminal:

o	A11_generafechacall.py
o	A12_generahoracall.py
o	A13_duracion_llamada.py

-	Next files give a result where are running from console or Terminal.

Names obey to a structure required by class project and follows the designation in order to run the entire program (e.g A/1/a designes the first part of the excercise of the point a. ):

  o	A1a_Genera_clave_simple.py: 
   Terminal or CMD running as: 
    >> Python A1a_Genera_clave_simple.py 

  o	A1bc_Generar_Clave_Cliente_aleatoria.py:
   Terminal or CMD running as:: 
>> Python A1bc_Generar_Clave_Cliente_aleatoria.py

  o A1d_Creacion_Fichero_Paises.py:
  Terminal or CMD running as::
 >> Python A1d_Creacion_Fichero_Paises.py

  o	A23_Generar_fichero_2020.py:
  Terminal or CMD running as::
 >> Python A23_Generar_fichero_2020.py 5000

Nota: En este caso 5000 es la variable del numero de registros que se quiera tener en el fichero. Debe ser un numero mayor de 0 y entero.

  o	A2a_Webscrapping.py:
Terminal or CMD running as:: 
>> Python A2a_Webscrapping.py

  o	A2b_Elimina_palabras.py:
Terminal or CMD running as:: 
>> Python A2b_Elimina_palabras.py

  o	A2c_Genera_Mensaje_Text.py
Terminal or CMD running as:: 
>> Python A2c_Genera_Mensaje_Text.py

In case of error: 
UnicodeDecodeError: 'utf-8' codec can't decode byte 0xf3 in position 21: invalid continuation byte. 
Please, change in line 35 to:
   with open('Corpus_palabras.txt',encoding='UTF-8') as corpus:

In case of execute the program from encoding UTF-8 in MacOs computers. Assert and Try exception are included in the code to      avoid this problem: 
   >>A2c_Genera_Mensaje_Text._encoding.py

  o	B4_Creacion_Matrices_Tarifas.py
  Terminal or CMD running as: 
  >> Python B4_Creacion_Matrices_Tarifas.py

  o	B5_Generar_Minutos_Ingresos_Totales.py
  Terminal or CMD running as: 
  >> Python B5_Generar_Minutos_Ingresos_Totales.py

  o	B6a_MapReduce_MinutosTotales.py
    Terminal or CMD running as: 
  >> Python B6a_MapReduce_MinutosTotales.py llamadas2020.txt

  o	B6b_MapReduce_IngresosTotales.py
    Terminal or CMD running as: 
  >> Python B6b_MapReduce_IngresosTotales.py llamadas2020.txt

